headline: New Partnership Brings Athletic Brewing Company's Non-Alcoholic Brews to 100+ Live Music Venues and Festivals
summary: Athletic Brewing Company, America's largest dedicated non-alcoholic brewer, is bringing its award-winning brews to the heart of the live music scene with an exciting new multi-year partnership. Athletic is now the official non-alcoholic beer partner for more than 100 Live Nation concert venues across the U.S., including renowned locations such as Brooklyn Paramount, Shoreline Amphitheatre, and The Gorge Amphitheatre.
